  Se3-kan sui-bong2 u7 loa7-choe7 chu7-choan e5 lang5, ka-ki7 khoa-khau2 chun2-chun2 tit-tioh8 kiu3, goa2 khiok m7-kaN2 an2-ni, tit-tioh8 kiu3 a2 boe7, si7 au7-lai5 e5 tai7-chi3. M7-kaN2 ke-kiam2 kong2 tek-khak tit-tioh8 kiu3-un, beh thai2 kaN2 kho3 ka-ki7 kong2 tit-tioh8 kiu3? Hit ho7 chu7-choan--e5 tek-khak bo5 siaN2 khiam-pi e5 sim, iah8 si7 chin kiau-ngou7, li2 siuN7 an2-ni m7 si7?” Goa2 in3 kong2, “Li2 na7 liah8 chun2-chun2 tit-tioh8 kiu3 choe3 chu7-choan, si7 bo5 tho3-tong3. Chit ho7 sim si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 ai3, iah8 si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 un2-chun2--e5. Ia5-sou kong2, ‘Goa2 sit8-sit8 ka7 lin2 kong2, ThiaN Goa2 e5 oe7, iah8 sin3 chhe Goa2--e5, chiu7 u7 eng2-oah8, boe7 kau3 siu7 sim2-phoaN3, si7 i2-keng chhut-si2 jip8 oah8--lah.’ (Iok-han7 5:24.) Li2 kong2, li2 chhim-chhim oa2-kho3 Ia5-sou ui7 li2 sou2 choe3--e5, li2 tok8-tok8 sin3-kho3 Ia5-sou na7-tiaN7?” Lau7-lang5 in3 kong2, “Si7, goa2 tok8-tok8 sin3-kho3 Ia5-sou, goa2 put-chi2 sin3 Kiu3 Chu2 e5 toa7 kong-lo5, Chu2 sou2 choe3 tak8 hang7 oan5-choan5 kau3-giah8, boe7 koh ke--tit-lah.” Goa2 chiu7 mng7 kong2, “Li2 chhim sin3 Ia5-sou sou2 choe3 e5 kong-lo5 i2-keng oan5-choan5 ho2, lan2 se3-kan lang5 boe7 ka7 I ke-thiN, chhi3 mng7, li2 koh ke e5 tui3-thai7 si7 chaiN2-iuN7? Ia5-sou e5 kong-lo5, tau3-ti2 lan2 oe7 ka7 I kiam2-chio2 a2 boe7? An2-ni tioh8 a2 m7 tioh8?” Lau7-lang5 kong2, “Li2 sou2 mng7, goa2 bo5 beng5 siaN2 i3-su3, li2 m7 sin3 seng3-tou5 tioh8 choe3 kau3 be2 chiah un2-tang3 oe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3--mah?” Goa2 in3, “Te7-it bo5 chu2-chhai5 e5 lang5 sim-lai7 bo5 tiaN7 bo5 tioh8, tok8-tok8 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3 eng2 boe7 koe2-oaN7. Sou2-i2 Chu2 po2-hou7 I keng2-soan2 e5 peh-siN3 ku2-tng5 bo5 soah. Na7 si7 te7-it seng3 chheng-khi3 e5 lang5, kan-ta oa2-kho3 ka-ki7 tiaN7 tioh8 e5 sim lai5 po2 sin khu, kiaN-liau2 chit si5 iah8 po2 boe7-tiau5, tek-khak tioh8 si2. Choe7-jin5 tit-tioh8 kiu3, tit-tioh8 pi3-iu7, si7 Siong7-te3 in2-chhoa7 in kau3 Ia5-sou e5 bin7-cheng5, u7 Ia5-sou kap Seng3-Sin5 e5 tiaN7-tioh8 e5 sim kou3-siu2--in, hou7 in boe7 hou7 Mou5-kui2 chhiuN2--khi3, che chiu7-si7 te7-it kian-kou3 e5 toe7-ki, si7 te7-it kau3-giah8 thang oa2-kho3--e5, li2 siuN7 si7 an2-ni m7 si7?” Lau7-lang5 hoaN-hi2 kong2, “Che chin-chiaN3 si7 te7-it un2-tang3 e5 toe7-ki. Goa2 chho3--lah, chho3--lah, giau5-gi5 Siong7-te3 pi2 sin3-kho3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 khah chu7-choan. Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 goa2 bo5 chhim-sin3, an2-ni kiam2 m7-si7 ka-ki7 liah8 choe3 ti3-hui7?” Chek-si5 kiah8 pit chiong “Ng3-bang7” koe2 choe3 chhim-sin3 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 toa7 kong-lo5, goa2 thang hou7 I chih-chiap chiuN7 thiN.” ChhiaN2 thok8-chia2 ti3-i3 thak8 Iok-han7 chap8-gou7 chiuN47 chap8 chat kau3 chap8-saN chat Soa3 kang2-kiu3 e7-phiN sou2 sia2 e5 si-ku3. 
