  Ia5-sou si7 ban7 ong5 e5 Ong5, ban7 Chu2 e5 Chu2, kang3-ke7 kap lan2 choe3 peng5-iu2, na2 hiaN-ti7, che kiam2 m7 si7 kek8 chun-kui3 eng5-kng? Se3-kan iau2 u7 chun-kui3 eng5-kng khah-iaN5 che--mah? Lan2 si7 choe7-jin5, si7 te7-it san3-chhiah bo5 te3 thang kong2 e5 lang5, Ia5-sou chiong I hu3-ju7 e5 un-tian2 siuN2-su3--lan2, chit ho7 un-tian2 se3-chiuN7 te7-it hu3-kui3--e5 iah8 bo5 te3 thang tit--tioh8, lan2 tit-tioh8 che kek8 po2-poe3 e5 un-tian2, sit8-chai7 pi2 se3-chiuN7 kek8 hu3-kui3--e5 khah hu3-kui3. Choe3 hong5-te3 e5 chhe-eng7 thang kong2 chin chun-kui3 eng5-kng, lang5-lang5 keng3--i, lan2 choe3 ban7 ong5 e5 Ong5 e5 chhe-eng7, kiam2 bo5 koh-khah chun-kui3? Sou2-i2 Seng3-keng kong2, “Thoan5 hok-im--e5, in e5 kha-pou7 siaN ho2 thiaN kau3 chaiN2-iuN7.” Ia5-sou chhut-si3 ti7 be2-cho5, si2 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3, li2 m7-thang siuN7 I siN pi-bi5, si2 kian3-siau3, na7 an2-ni phah-sng3, thai2 oe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3? Li2 m7-thang kan-ta siuN7 Ia5-sou pi-bi5 e5 si5, tioh8 beng5-beng5 chai Ia5-sou te7-it chun-kui3 eng5-kng e5 si5, chiaN5-choe3 lang5 e5 sin-the2, te7-it pi-bi5 e5 si5, iah8 u7 Siong7-te3 e5 seng3-chit, chit-tiap8 tiam3 ti7 thiN--nih8 che7 Siong7-te3 e5 toa7-peng5, I iu5-goan5 teh the2-thiap lang5 e5 loan2-jiok8. Ia5-sou e5 oe7 si7 thiN-teng2 e5 lut8-hoat, I e5 ku2-tong7 si7 sin5-jiah, I e5 kiaN5-choe3 si7 lan2 oan5-choan5 e5 bou5-iuN7, I si2, chiu7-si7 hi-seng choe3 che3-mih8, koh-oah8, si7 thai5-iaN5 kui2-ong5, koh lim5-kau3, thiN-teng2 e5 thian-kun tek-khak choe3 I e5 chhe-eng7, te7-gek8 e5 Mou5-kui2 iah8 long2 kiaN-hiaN5, kiN3-na7 siu7 siok8 e5 seng3-tou5 long2 hou7 I kiu3, tim5-lun5 e5 lang5 long2 tioh8 hou7 I sim2-phoaN3. 
  Na2 Chui2 Hiah Chheng, Na2 Seh Hiah Peh8. 
  Chit8 jit8 u7 siN3 TiuN kap siN3 Li2--e5 nng7 lang5 teh tam5-lun7 to7-li2, siN3 TiuN--e5 kong2, “Lan2 oa2-kho3 Ki-tok e5 huih, eng2-oan2 sia3-bian2 choe7-ok, I sui si7 chit8 pai2 sia3-bian2, lan2 chiu7-si7 tiaN7-tiaN7 bo5 choe7.” SiN3 Li2 e5 kong2, “Lang5 kiam2 oe7 chai choe7-ok u7 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2? Goa2 siuN7 siN-cheng5 kaN2 m7-chai. Siat-su2 lang5 bo5 choe7, chiu7 thang na2 chui2 hiah chheng, na2 seh hiah peh8, se3-kan lang5 thai2 oe7 an2-ni? Goa2 khoaN3 lang5 ka-ki7 kong2 i choe7 tit-tioh8 sia3--e5, chin toa7 chho3-gou7, iah8 si7 phin2-phong2 e5 oe7.” Lang5 mi5--si5 cheng7-cheng7 to2 ti7 bin5-chhng5, kiam2 oe7 chai i e5 choe7-ok i2-keng tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2? Siat-su2 ti7 kim-mi5 ke3-si3, thai2 oe7 chai i e5 choe7-ok tek-khak bian2 siu7 chek-hoat8, bian2 loh8 te7-gek8? Lang5 beh thai3 oe7 chai? ChhiaN2 khoaN3 Siong7-te3 e5 chheh, khoaN3 I e5 oe7 kong2 chaiN2-iuN7. 
  “Sou2-i2 hiah-e5 tiam3 ti7 Ki-tok Ia5-sou--e5, taN long2 bo5 teng7 choe7.” (Lo5-ma2 8: 1.) “Goa2 sia3-bian2 lin2 e5 choe7.” (Sat-ka-li7-a 3:4.) “Goa2 sit8-sit8 ka7 lin2 kong2, thiaN Goa2 e5 oe7, bian2 siu7 sim2-phoaN3, chiu7-si7 i2-keng chhut si2 jip8 oah8.” (Iok-han7 5:24.) “Goa2 koat-toan3 bo5 koh ki3-liam7 in e5 choe7-ok kap in e5 put-hoat.” (Hi-pek-lai5 10:17.) “Phi3-ju7 tang li7-khui sai, tu5 goa2 e5 choe7-ok, bo5 ka7 goa2 chek-hoat8.” (Si-phian 105[103]:12.) “Goa2 chhat-siau li2 e5 choe7, na2 koaN2 bat8-hun5.” (I2-sai3-a 44:22.) KhoaN3 sou2 in2 e5 Seng3-keng sui si7 kui2-chat na7-tiaN7, iah8 kau3-giah8 thang cheng3-beng5 lan2 sou2 sin3--e5, m7 si7 lam7-sam2 ka-ki7 phin2-phong2, Seng3-keng lai7 u7 Siong7-te3 sou2 kong2 kui2-ku3 e5 oe7, kau3-giah8 thang in2-cheng3. Lan2 tioh8 chai lan2 sou2 sin3--e5 si7 chi7-chui7, chiu7-si7 chai lan2 bo5 ka-ki7 phin2-phong2, sit8-chai7 u7 chin e5 pin5-ku3, lan2 ti7 sim2-phoaN3 e5 si5, chhim-sin3 Ia5-sou sou2 choe3 e5 kang, oe7 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 cho7-ui7 cheng5, cho7-chiu7 lan2, chhat-biat8 choe7-ok, bo5 li5-si-a2 ha5-chhu5. Lang5 kan-ta kong2, goa2 ng3-bang7 oe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3, lan2 si7 kiaN5 chiaN3-lou7--e5, m7-ku2 in sim-lai7 bo5 pa2-ak, chu7-jian5 Siong7-te3 boe7 ko-seng--i, hou7 i khia7-khi2 ti7 I e5 sou2-chai7. 
  Tit-tioh8 Kiu3 u7 Beng5 e5 Cheng3-kiN3. 
  “Chu2 kong2, chiah-e5 jit8 i2-au7, Goa2 kap in sou2 beh lip8 e5 iok si7 chit-e5, Goa2 beh chiong Goa2 e5 lut8-hoat he7 ti7 in e5 sim, khek ti7 in e5 thau5-nau2, au7--lai5 chiu7 kong2, In e5 choe7-ok, in e5 put-hoat, koat-toan3 bo5 koh ki3-liam7.” Chiah-e5 ki3-jian5 sia3-bian2, chiu7 bo5 koh ui7-tioh8 choe7 hian3-che3. Sou2-i2 hiaN-ti7--ah, lan2 ti7 Ia5-sou e5 huih ki3-jian5 tit-tioh8 ho2-taN2 jip8 seng3-sou2, tui3 I sou2 ka7 lan2 khui sin koh oah8 e5 lou7, an3 tiuN3-li5 keng-ke3--e5, chit-e5 tiuN3-li5 chiu7-si7 I e5 sin-the2, koh ki3-jian5 u7 toa7 che3-si ti7-li2 Siong7-te3 e5 ke, lan2 tioh8 eng7 chin-sit8 e5 sim, chhiong-moa2 e5 sin3, sim i2-keng siu7 hiu3, bian2 hou7 liong5-sim chek-pi7, seng-khu iah8 i2-keng siu7 chheng-chui2 soe2, lai5 chhin-kun7 Siong7-te3. Lan2 sou2 ng3-bang7--e5, i2-keng u7 seng5-jin7, taN tioh8 kian-kou3 chit-e5 seng5-jin7 bo5 io5-tang7, in-ui7 hit-e5 eng3-un2 lan2--e5 si7 chin-sit8.” (Hi-pek-lai5 10:16-23.) “In-ui7 lang5 si7 ki2 khah toa7--e5 lai5 chiu3-choa7, iah8 eng7 chiu3-choa7 choe3 saN-chiN e5 kiat-be2, lai5 koat-tiaN7 i. An2-ni, Siong7-te3 ai3 beh kek-goa7 hian2-beng5 I e5 chi2-i3 boe7 i5-ek8, hou7 hiah-e5 seng5-chiap eng3-un2 e5 lang5 chai, chiah eng7 chiu3-choa7 lai5 choe3 cheng3-kiN3, beh tui3 nng7 hang7 boe7 i5-ek8 e5 su7, Siong7-te3 sou2 boe7-oe7 peh8-chhat8--e5, hou7 lan2 u7 toa7-toa7 e5 an-ui3, chiu7-si7 lan2 i2-keng to5-pi7 lai5 khiN5 sou2 he7 ti7 thau5-cheng5 e5 ng3-bang7. Lan2 u7 chit-e5 ng3-bang7, chhin-chhiuN7 leng5-hun5 e5 tiaN3, pha ti7 tiuN3-li5 lai7, kian-kou3 bo5 i5-soa2, Ia5-sou choe3 sian-hong, i2-keng ui7-tioh8 lan2 jip8-khi3 hia, chiaN5-choe3 eng2-oan2 e5 Che3-si-tiuN2, chiau3 Bek8-ki-se2-tek e5 pan-liat8.” (Hi-pek-lai5 6:16-20.) “Goa2 sia2 chiah-e5 hou7 lin2 sin3 Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2 e5 mia5--e5, beh hou7 lin2 chai lin2 u7 eng2-oah8.” ( Iok-han7 5 :13.) 
  Ma2-teng Lou7-tek Kap Sat-tan3 Pian7-lun7 Choe7-ok. 
  Ma2-teng Lou7-tek si7 Kai2-cheng3-kau3 e5 thau5 chit8 lang5, i chit mi5 bang7-kiN3 khoaN3-kiN3 Sat-tan3 theh8 chit8 kng2 chin tng5 e5 chheh, khui hou7 i khoaN3, Lou7-tek khoaN3 ji7 put-chi2 soe3, choa7 put-chi2 bat8, chiu7 soe3-ji7 thak8, thak8 liau2, to si7 ki3 i e5 choe7-ok--liau2-liau2, lian5 chit8 hang7 bo5 hoan7-tioh8--e5 iah8 bo5, tui3 cha2 i2-keng boe7 ki3--tit e5 choe7-ok iah8 ki3--teh, bo5 chit8 pai2 phah-ka-lauh8. Lou7-tek chiong sou2 ki3 e5 choe7-ok, chit8-tiau5 chit8-tiau5 siong5-se3 chha5-kho2--i, mng7 Sat-tan3 kong2, “Che tak8-tiau5 long2 si7 goa2 sou2 hoan7 e5 choe7 m7 si7?” Sat-tan3 kong2, “Li2 bat hoan7--bo5?” Lou7-tek kong2, “Goa2 na7 bat hoan7--tioh8, tioh8 chiong goa2 it-chhe3 sou2 hoan7 e5 choe7-ok kau goa2 khoaN3.” Sat-tan3 chek-si5 khi3 theh8 koh chit8 kng2 kap tu2-chiah siang7-khoan2 e5 lai5, lai7-bin7 iah8 sia2 put-chi2 chat8, kap hit kng2 bo5 li5-a2 cheng-chha. Lou7-tek koh tak8 tiau5 seng2-chhat, sou2 ki3 long2 si7 sit8, mng7 Sat-tan3 kong2, “Che long2 si7 goa2 hoan7 e5 choe7--mah?” Sat-tan3 in3, “Si7. Li2 sou2 hoan7--e5 chim-chiok siuN7 khoaN3, li2 ho7 choe3 Kai2-cheng3-kau3 e5 thau5-lang5, li2 e5 choe7-ok kau3 chiah choe7 tiau5, li2 u7 siaN2 bin7-bak8 kiN3 Siong7-te3, thoe3 Siong7-te3 choe3 kang?” Lou7-tek kong2, “Ho2. Li2 kiah8 pit hou7--goa2.” Eng7 ang5-bak8-chui2 hoaiN5 sia2 ti7 kng3--nih8, kong2, “Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 huih soe2-chheng goa2 it-chhe3 e5 choe7.” KhoaN3 chheh--e5, chhi3 siuN7, Li2 oe7 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 eng7 Chu2 e5 huih, chiong li2 e5 choe7 soe2 kau3 chheng-chheng khi3-khi3 a2-boe7? 
  Khek-liu5-pa-thoat-liap8 e5 Ki3-liam7 Pi. 
  Khek-liu5-pa-thoat-liap8 si7 kou2-cha2 e5 Ai-kip8 ong5 O2-liu5-tek e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2. Lang5 sui2 koh gau5, chap8-poeh he3 e5 si5 lau7-pe7 si2, siu7 beng7-leng7 soa3-chiap choe3 ong5, tng choe3 ong5 e5 si5 u7 khia7 chit8 ki ki3-liam7 pun2-sin e5 chioh8-pi, chap8-goa7 tng7 koaiN5, cho7 tng7 goa7 khoah. Pi--nih8 phah ji7 kong2-khi2 lu2-ong5 e5 chun-kui3 eng5-kng ti7 hit teng2-bin7. 1877 ni5 Ai-kip8 cheng3-hu2 chiong hit ki pi sang3 Eng-kok, Eng-kok tiau5-ti5 pi7-pan7 chun5 chai3 kau3 Lun5-tun. Chit ki pi cha2 khia7 ti7 Ai-kip8 Ni5-lo5 ho5 piN. Eng-kok khia7 chit ki pi e5 si5, tai7-seng pi7-pan7 chit8 te3 toa7 chioh8-bo7, tiong-ng chhak8-khang he7 kui2-na7 hang7 mih8 kap si3 kok bun5-ji7 e5 Seng3-chheh si3 pun2, koh u7 hoan-ek8 choe3 115 kok khiuN-khau2 e5 Seng3-keng chit8 chat he7 ti7 lai7-bin7. SiaN2-su7 he7 hiah-e5 mih8? In-ui7 lang5 siuN7 te7-it ki5-koai3 e5 chioh8-pi, nng7 chheng ni5 cheng5 khia7 ti7 Ai-kip8, taN soa2 chit8 ban7 li2 kau3 Eng-kok. Pi-nih8 sou2 phah e5 Ai-kip8 ji7, hian7-si5 bo5 lang5 bat. Chi7-chui7 bo5 siuN7 kou2-cha2 lang5 sou2 choe3 e5 ki5-iN7, chhim-chhim kiaN-liau2 nng7 chheng ni5 au7 chit ki pi to2, au7-tai7 e5 lang5 tek-khak beh liah8 sou2 he7 e5 mih8 choe3 po2-poe3. Chhi3 mng7 hoan-ek8 choe3 115 kok oe7 e5 Seng3-keng chat si7 ta2-loh8 chit8 chat? Chiu7-si7 Iok-han7 saN chiuN 16 chat. Cha2-jit8 Lou7-tek bat kong2, “Seng3-keng choan5 pun2 e5 i3-gi7 long2 pau-ham5 ti7 chit chat e5 lai7-bin7.” Chiu7-si7 sia2 kong2:
  In-ui7 Siong7-te3 chiong tok8-siN e5 KiaN2 siuN2-su3 se3-kan, hou7 kiN3-na7 sin3 I e5 lang5 boe7 tim5-lun5, oe7 tit tioh8 eng2-oah8, I thiaN3 se3-kan kau3 an2-ni. 
  Chit toe5 tai7-seng kong2 e5 ji7 si7 “Siong7-te3.” Iau3-kin2 e5 sou2-chai7 si7 “Siong7-te3 e5 thiaN3.” Sou2 siuN2-su3 se3-kan lang5--e5, chiu7-si7 “Ia5-sou Ki-tok.” Sou2 eng3-un2--e5, “eng2-oah8,” sou2 pau-ham5--e5 chiu7-si7 “Thong se3-kai3 e5 lang5.” Che kiam2 m7-si7 te7-it ki5-biau7--e5-mah? 
  Chui3-han3 e5 Kiu3-ioh8. 
  Bi2-kok bou2 siaN5 chit8 e5 chui3-han3, kiN3-tioh8 chiu2 chiu7 lim, lim tioh8 kau3 chui3, chui3 au7 tek-khak khi2 kong5, lam7-sam2 kiaN5, lam7-sam2 choe3, chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni 31 ni5 ku2--lah. Chiu2-chui3--e5 ki3-jian5 bo5 chu7-tiong7, chiu7 lang5 iah8 bo5 chun-tiong7--i, i poaN3-si3-lang5 choe3 chiu2-lou5, put-ko3 tak8 jit8 chai to2 ti7 chiu2-ang3 kha khun3, bo5 siuN7 beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3 lang5, u7 chiN5 tioh8 lai5 lim, bo5 chiah sia khiam3, it-bi7 siuN7 chiu2, ki5-u5 e5 tai7-chi3 m7 chai liau2-liau2, ke-lai7 e5 pe7-bu2, bou2-kiaN2 pang3 choe3 bo5 iau3-kin2. I e5 pe7-bu2 in-ui7 hau7-siN ai3 chiah8 chiu2, jit8-mi5 koah tng5 kho3 tou7, sin-khu pun2-jian5 iong2-kiaN7 u7 lat8, chong2-si7 be7 lau7 chiu7 si2. I e5 bou2 in-ui7 tiong7-hu tak8 jit8 chiu2-chui3, khou2-khng3 bo5 chhai2 kang, ang-bou2 ki3-jian5 boe7 ho5-hai5, iu7 koh sit-loh8 chiong-sin sou2 ng3-bang7, sim chin-chiaN3 sng, khoaN3-kiN3 lang5 e5 kiaN2-ji5 hiah chiaN5-iuN7, boe7 kim3 tit kam2-chhiok ka-ki7 m7 chhin-chhiuN7 lang5, toa7 kiaN2 hau2 iau, soe3 kiaN2 hau2 koaN5, bo5 lat8 thang iuN2-chhi7, an2-ni iu-bun7 ti3 piN7, 35 he3 chiu7 si2. I e5 kiaN2 cha-bou2-kiaN2 in-ui7 bo5 te3 oa2-toa3, iah8 siu7 khou2 tiong e5 kan-khou2. Au7--lai5 chit-e5 chui3-han3 thiaN-kiN3 sip8-ji7-ke3 e5 to7-li2, chai Ia5-sou thiaN3--i, teh theng3-hau7 i koe2-piN3, i chiu7 chai pun2-sin u7 choe7, hoan2-hoe2 kai2 chiu2, chit8 tih iah8 m7 jip8 chhui3, beh chit8 sim oa2-kho3 Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih, lai5 chin2-kiu3 I e5 sin-khu leng5-hun5. Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih chiu7-si7 chui3-han3 e5 toa7 kiu3-ioh8, oa2-kho3 Ia5-sou e5 huih, bo5 lun7 toa7 phaiN2 e5 lang5, long2 oe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3, sui-bong2 choe7-choe7 ni5 hou7 choe7-ok pe2-pak8, Ia5-sou oe7 pang3--i, in-ui7 Ia5-sou koan5-lek8 bo5 han7, kau3-giah8 chin2-kiu3 se3-kan kek8 phaiN2 e5 choe7-jin5. 
  Lam5-pak Bi2-chiu Chian3-tin7 e5 Seng5-chek. 
  (TIAM2-MIA5) 
  1860 ni5 kau3 1865 ni5, chi2 gou7 ni5 ku2 e5 tiong-kan, Lam5-Pak Bi2-chiu kau-chian3 chin siong-tiong7, tak8 pai2 kau-chian3 si2 ti7 chian3-tin7--nih8-e5 chin choe7. Chit8 jit8 kau-chian3 ke3-sin, si2--e5, tioh8-siong--e5 boe7 sng3--tit, hit si5 u7 nng7 ui7 bok8-su khi3 chian3-tin7 tham3-khoaN3 chiah-e5 lang5, hoan7-na7 khoaN3-kiN3 beh si2 be7 si2 e5 lang5, chiu7 aN3-loh8 soe3 siaN khou2-khng3 i tioh8 oa2-kho3 Chu2, kong2 “Peng5-iu2--ah, Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih oe7 soe2 chheng se3-kan lang5 e5 choe7, hou7 lan2 keng-ke3 ou-am3 e5 se3-kai3, leng5-hun5 kau3 kng-beng5 e5 sou2-chai7, hiong2-siu7 thian-tong5 ku2-tng5 e5 khoai3-lok8.” Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni sun5 kau3 hia kong2 kau3 hia. Lou7-be2 hng7-hng7 khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 e5 to2-teh khun3, tioh8-siong put-chi2 tang7, khoaN3 i e5 sin-the2 si3-chiaN3, chai si7 chit8 e5 iong2-kam2 e5 lang5, i e5 bin7-sek chhiN-peh8, phah-sng3 kaN2 i2-keng ke3-khui3, kun7-oa2 khoaN3-kiN3 sin-khu lioh8-a2 tin2-tang7, bok8-su chiu7 aN3-loh8 ng3 i e5 hi7-khang kong2, “HiaN-ti7--ah, Li2 tioh8 oa2-kho3 Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih oe7 soe2-chheng li2 tak8-ho7 e5 choe7.” Tioh8-siong--e5 io5-thau5 kah in boh8-tit choe3 siaN, bok8-su phah-sng3 i boe7 beng5 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7, sou2-i2 koh teng5-chai3 ka7 i kong2-beng5, siu7-siong--e5 bian2-kiong2 in3 kong2, “ChhiaN2 boh8-tit choe3 siaN, goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 loa7-choe7 kau-chian3 e5 lang5, tiap8-a2-ku2 pai5-liat8 ti7 kiong-chhong, thiN-sai3 theh8 oah8-mia7 chheh teh tiam2 mia5, goa2 tu2-tu2 teh tiuN-ti5 thiaN kio3 goa2 e5 mia5.” Chhui-chhek siu7-siong--e5 e5 i3-su3, liah8 choe3 kio3 mia5-ji7 chiu7 thang chiuN7 thian-tong5, siat-su2 oah8-mia7 chheh--nih8 bo5 mia5--e5 chiu7 boe7 chiuN7 thian-tong5. I kong2 soah, bak8-chiu khoeh-khoeh khun3--khi3, giam2-jian5 teh chu3-i3 thiaN chit8-iuN7. U7 tiap8-a2-ku2, i hoaN-hoaN hi2-hi2 toa7-siaN in3 “Chai7,” in3 liau2 chiu7 ke3-khui3. KhoaN3 chheh--e5, li2 beh siuN7 chit lang5 ke3-ong2, chin thang kho2-lin5, na7-si7 tui3 goan2 khoaN3 sit8-chai7 m7-si7 an2-ni, in-ui7 i e5 mia5 cha2-cha2 ki3 ti7 oah8-mia7 chheh, sou2-i2 si2 e5 si5 chit8 e7 kau3, chiu7 thiaN kiN3 thiN-sai3 kio3 i e5 mia5, siat-su2 i na7 choe3 lang5 bu5 ok put-chok, thiN-sai3 thai2 beh kio3--i. Lang5 oah8 ti7 se3-kan, chhin-chhiuN7 bin5-bang7, siN3-mia7 cha2-khi2 boe7 po2 kau3 e7-hng, lan2 e5 si2-ki5 m7-chai siaN2 si5 beh kau3, lan2 boe7 tai7-seng chai, sou2-i2 tioh8 koaN2-kin2 chiong lan2 e5 mia5 ki3 ti7 oah8-mia7 chheh, kau3 si2 e5 si5 kau3, thiN-sai3 chiu7 thang kio3 lan2 e5 mia5. Lan2 na7 siuN7 mia5 i2-keng sia2 chiuN7 oah8-mia7 chheh, koh-khah tioh8 si5-si5 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, khian5-seng5 hok8-sai7 Chu2, chiong seng-khu leng5-hun5 hian3 hou7 Chu2 Ia5-sou, hou7 lan2 bo5 chit8 hang7 bo5 piau2-beng5 Chu2 e5 chun-kui3 eng5-kng. 
  Si3-liap8 Beng5-chu. 
  Beng5-chu si7 te7-it po2-poe3 e5 mih8, se3-kan lang5-lang5 ai3, chong2-si7 beng5-chu u7 si5 oe7 phah-phaiN2, u7 si5 oe7 sit-loh8, iah8 u7 si5 sou2 tit-tioh8 m7-si7 chin--e5, a2-si7 bo5 ho2--e5, in-ui7 si7 u7 heng5 e5 but8-chit, sou2-i2 sui-jian5 po2-poe3, iu5-goan5 bo5 kau3-giah8 liah8 choe3 kui3-khi3. Hok-im chin-li2 si7 bo5 heng5 e5 beng5-chu, i e5 po2-poe3 bo5 mih8 thang pi2, se3-kan lang5 tak8 e5 liah8 beng5-chu choe3 po2-poe3, sou2-i2 chioh che lai5 pi2-pheng7, sit8-chai7 iu5-goan5 pi2 boe7 tioh8. 
  Kiu3 lang5 e5 to7-li2 sui-bong2 m7-si7 beng5-chu sou2 oe7 pi2--tit, chong2-si7 iah8 u7 pau-ham5 beng5-chu e5 i3-su3 ti7 lai7-bin7. Pun choe3 si3-hang7 lai5 kong2. Te7 it liap8 beng5-chu chiu7-si7 “OAN5-BOAN2 sia3-bian2.” Siong7-te3 chiong lan2 lang5 e5 choe7-ok, oan5-boan2 sia3-bian2, bo5 lun7 choe7-ok loa7 chhim-tang7, I long2 it-lut8 sia3-bian2, hou7 lan2 bo5 si-ho5 khiam3-kheh. Ti7 I Iok-han7 1:7 kong2, “Eng7 I e5 KiaN2 Ia5-sou e5 huih soe2-chheng lan2 long2-chong2 e5 choe7.” Siong7-te3 sia3-bian2 lang5 it-chhe3 e5 put-hoat, put-gi7, che kiam2 boe7 thang kong2, Oan5-boan2 sia3-bian2--mah? 
  Te7 ji7 liap8 beng5-chu chiu7-si7 “PEH8-PEH8 TIT-TIOH8 e5 sia3-bian2.” Seng3-keng kong2, “Goa2 tu5 lin2 e5 choe7, m7-si7 in-ui7 lin2 chiah an2-ni, sit8-chai7 Goa2 e5 i3-su3 beh sia3-bian2--lin2, bo5 koh-iuN7 eng7 mih8 peh8-peh8 siuN2-su3--lin2, sou2-i2 Goa2 sia3-bian2--lang5, si7 Goa2 ka-ki7 e5 sim-goan7.” Thang chai Siong7-te3 sia3-bian2 choe7-jin5, m7-si7 in-ui7 choe7-jin5 siu tek-heng7, kam2-tong7 Siong7-te3 lai5 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2, si7 oan5-choan5 chhut ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 i3-su3, si7 I ka-ki7 e5 sim-goan7. I sou2 kong2 “ka-ki7” si7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3? Chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 e5 thiaN3-sim. Sou2-i2 Au-chiu tak8 kok e5 ji7 koe2-seh “Sia3-bian2” choe3 “peh8-peh8 tit--tioh8” e5 i3-su3. 
  Te7 saN liap8 beng5-chu chiu7-si7 “OAN5-CHOAN5 sia3-bian2.” Che m7 si7 ti7 chit si5 sia3-bian2 chiah ke-thiN hit si5 e5 i3-su3, koh m7-si7 kin-a2-jit8 sia3-bian2 lang5 e5 choe7, chiah koh ti7 bin5-a2-jit8 ki3 ti7 phou7-nih8. Seng3-chheh kong2, “KiN3-na7 seng3-tou5 e5 choe7-ok, na7 tit-tioh8 Chu2 lin5-bin2, tu5-biat8 che7-koa3, si7 na2 chiong it-chhe3 e5 choe7-ok hiat ti7 chhim-ian.” 
  Te7 si3 liap8 beng5-chu chiu7-si7 “HIAN7-CHAI7 sia3-bian2.” Che si7 siok8 ti7 hian7-chai7 e5 hok-khi3, m7 si7 siok8 ti7 chiong-lai5 e5 ng3-bang7, si7 be7 hian2-beng5 e5 li7-ek. Phi3-ju7 kin-a2-jit8 tit-tioh8 san2-giap8, chu7-jian5 bian2 theng3-hau7 si2 e5 si5 chiah tit-tioh8 chit-e5 sia3-bian2. 
  Hiah-e5 m7 sin3 to7-li2--e5, long2 m7 chai sia3-bian2 e5 li2, in phah-sng3 kiam2-chhai2 beh si2 e5 si5 oe7 hiau-heng7 tit-tioh8 un-tian2, long2 m7 chai se3-kan lang5 thang ti7 siN-cheng5, khak-sit8 chai choe7 i2-keng tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2. Koh in kan-ta ng3-bang7 kau3 si2 e5 si5, kiam2-chhai2 thang tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 un-tian2, long2 m7 chai bo5 lun7 oah8 si2, long2 thang hiong2-siu7 Siong7-te3 e5 un-tian2, chiong it-chhe3 sou2 hoan7 e5 choe7, choe3 chit8-e7 i2-keng sia3-bian2 lah. 
  Kiu3 lang5 e5 to7-li2 chhin-chhiuN7 bo7, u7 si3-liap8 po2-poe3 sia3-bian2 e5 beng5-chu tio3 ti7 cheng5-au7, i e5 sui2 kau3 chaiN2-iuN7? KhoaN3 chheh e5 peng5-iu2, lan2 long2 si7 u7 choe7, choe7-ok chhim tang7, siat-su2 bo5 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 sia3-bian2, chiu7 chin thang hoan5-lo2, sou2-i2 sia3-bian2 kap lan2 lang5 u7 toa7 koan-he7. TaN lan2 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 chiah oe7 tit-tioh8 chit-e5 kiu3-un? Chiu7-si7 tioh8 oa2-kho3 Ia5-sou chiah oe7 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2. 
  Lek8-su2 Kap Chhim-sin3 e5 Hun-piat.
  U7 chit8 e5 chhou-chhou sin3 to7-li2 e5 lang5 kong2: Li2 na7 sin3 Ia5-sou si2 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3, put-ko3 si7 lek8-su2 chit8 hang7 sit8-su7, chiu7 ti7 bo5 phah bo5 sng3 e5 tiong-kan u7 tit-tioh8 kiu3 lang5 e5 hau7-giam7. Li2 oe7 sin3 Ia5-sou thoe3 li2 si2 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3, che chiu7-si7 chhim-sin3 e5 kang-hu, chiu7-si7 toa7-toa7 u7 kiu3 lang5 e5 leng5-lek8, bo5 lun7 siaN2 lang5, u7 chit ho7 chhim-sin3, long2 thang tit-tioh8 kiu3. KhoaN3 chit lang5 khi2-thau5 sin3 to7-li2, oe7 kong2 chit ho7 oe7, thang chai i i2-keng beng5-pek8 kiu3 lang5 e5 hong-hoat--lah, sui si7 Po2-lo5 sian-siN iah8 bo5 kong2 kau3 chiah beng5 e5 to7-li2. 
